### Health
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### Customer login
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/customer-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobile": "9876543210"
}

### Verify OTP
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobile": "9876543210",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### Products
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products

### Product by barcode
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products/barcode/8901063150853

### Create cart
POST http://localhost:4000/api/cart/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "replace-user-id"
}

### Add item
POST http://localhost:4000/api/cart/add-item
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartId": "replace-cart-id",
  "barcode": "8901063150853",
  "quantity": 1
}

### IoT weight reading
POST http://localhost:4000/api/iot/weight
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartId": "replace-cart-id",
  "weightKg": 0.532,
  "deviceId": "esp32-scale-01"
}

### Verify weight
POST http://localhost:4000/api/weight/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartId": "replace-cart-id",
  "actualWeightKg": 0.532
}

### UPI payment
POST http://localhost:4000/api/payment/upi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartId": "replace-cart-id",
  "upiId": "raj123@okaxis"
}

### Generate bill
POST http://localhost:4000/api/bills/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartId": "replace-cart-id"
}
